summary: I haven’t really paid attention to how much I’ve posted on this blog, but over 1000 posts??? That’s crazy! Especially since the...
body:
I haven’t really paid attention to how much I’ve posted on this blog, but over 1000 posts??? That’s crazy! Especially since the vast majority of those posts are content I’ve created.

I was going through some of my old posts today, and I kinda miss some of the content I’ve done in the past like ships, drabbles, those bullet point lists etc. So y’know, if you guys wanna send requests for stuff that I don’t typically do, feel free to send them in (not selca ships tho, I don’t like judging by looks in any situation).

I might not do everything, if it’s something I feel uncomfortable doing, or something I don’t think I actually can do. But if you don’t send it on anon, I can at least tell that I’m not doing it or why. I’ll try to do most things tho, because I hate disappointing you guys.

So feel free to send in requests for drabbles, fake texts, ships, general questions about me/the boys/life, random asks, or just whatever you want me to do! xx

title: That Sinking Feeling
body:
read it on the AO3 at https://ift.tt/2N91tkk

by bethanym09

The daring glint in Namjoon’s eyes as he steps closer, right into Yoongi’s personal space, is almost too much. Instead of backing down, Yoongi takes half a step closer, meeting the challenge. Yoongi’s heart rejoices when he realizes that he hadn’t been imagining the gazes full of want coming from the taller man throughout the night. His pulse is picking up fast as he meets Namjoon’s gaze with a smirk. It’s at that moment with Namjoon looming over him, eyes scanning Yoongi like a full course meal, that Yoongi decides there is probably nothing Namjoon wants to take that he isn’t willing to give…after proves he can handle him that is.
Namjoon looks just as effected by their proximity as Yoongi, and his eyes trail down purposefully to Yoongi’s throat. The longing between them is practically tangible.
“Do you have a safeword Yoongi? I wouldn’t want to hurt you unless you really want it.”

reblog.comment: So I watched the BTS Jimmy Fallon and GMA stuff and I’m just so proud… like watching no more dream and bulletproof pt 2 I could never have imagined this… hold me ARMY fam 😭😭😭…. and now, like yoongi says… onto GRAMMYS NEXT !!!!!

trail.content_raw: So I watched the BTS Jimmy Fallon and GMA stuff and I’m just so proud… like watching no more dream and bulletproof pt 2 I could never have imagined this… hold me ARMY fam 😭😭😭…. and now, like yoongi says… onto GRAMMYS NEXT !!!!!
trail.content: So I watched the BTS Jimmy Fallon and GMA stuff and I’m just so proud… like watching no more dream and bulletproof pt 2 I could never have imagined this… hold me ARMY fam 😭😭😭…. and now, like yoongi says… onto GRAMMYS NEXT !!!!!
